media:group.media:title: How Friday Night Funkin' Blew Up Out of Nowhere
media:group.media:description:
In today's video, we dive into the history and controversy of one of the most popular games of the last year. Do you like Friday Night Funkin'? Why do you think it got so popular? Let me know in the comments below.
